    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks. i guess it depends on what people prioritize, but like, given how fast climate change is happening, do you think there's actually a realistic way to hit net zero targets without some kind of major expansion in nuclear? or is it just too slow/risky compared to everything else?",
      "source": "evaluator"
