    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "that seems pretty definitive. so you're saying it's basically a requirement? some people argue that investing in nuclear is just a distraction that sucks up money and time that should be going toward battery storage and solar/wind instead. if we don't expand nuclear, aren't we just making the climate crisis worse because we won't hit our goals in time?",
